'''Mikorzyn''' {{IPAr|pl|m|i|'|k|o|<U+017C>|y|n}} is a [[village]] in the administrative district of [[Gmina K<U+0119>pno]], within [[K<U+0119>pno County]], [[Greater Poland Voivodeship]], in west-central Poland.<ref name="TERYT">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.pl/broker/access/prefile/listPreFiles.jspa |title=Central Statistical Office (GUS) - TERYT (National Register of Territorial Land Apportionment Journal) |date=2008-06-01 |language=Polish}}</ref>

